---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="POCN — Case Study">

  <div class="section">
    <a class="breadcrumb" href="/work/">← <span>Case Studies</span> / POCN</a>
    <div class="cs-hero">[Redacted campaign dashboard or media plan graphic]</div>
    <div class="cs-tags"><span class="cs-tag">Performance</span><span class="cs-tag">Healthcare</span><span class="cs-tag">Programmatic</span><span class="cs-tag">HCP Marketing</span></div>
    <div class="cs-title">Pharma media across 50+ therapies in a regulated HCP environment</div>
    <div class="cs-subtitle">Two years as the sole programmatic strategist managing $1.7M+ in media spend across up to 30 concurrent campaigns and 50+ pharmaceutical therapies for J&amp;J, Eli Lilly, AbbVie, and Regeneron — while leading a DSP migration that drove significant annual cost savings.</div>
    <div class="cs-meta-card">
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Client</div><div class="cs-meta-value">POCN</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Duration</div><div class="cs-meta-value">May 2022 – Jul 2024</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Role</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Digital Marketing Manager</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Industry</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Healthcare / Pharma</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="stat-strip">
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">$1.7M+</div><div class="stat-label">Total media spend managed</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">50+</div><div class="stat-label">Pharma therapies supported</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">30</div><div class="stat-label">Concurrent campaigns managed</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Context · Action · Result</div>
    <div class="car-grid">
      <div class="car-sidebar">
        <div class="car-step active" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-pocn-1')"><div class="car-step-label">01 · Context</div><div class="car-step-title">The situation</div></div>
        <div class="car-step" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-pocn-2')"><div class="car-step-label">02 · Action</div><div class="car-step-title">What I did</div></div>
        <div class="car-step" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-pocn-3')"><div class="car-step-label">03 · Result</div><div class="car-step-title">What it produced</div></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div id="car-pocn-1" class="car-content">
          <div class="car-content-label">01 · Context</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">Narrow clinical audience, strict compliance, and a platform migration — all at once.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">POCN connects pharmaceutical brands with Nurse Practitioner and Physician Assistant audiences. Campaigns spanned 50+ therapies across oncology, immunology, CNS, cardiovascular, and rare disease — for J&amp;J, Eli Lilly, AbbVie, and Regeneron. Every asset required MLR review before deployment. Audience pools were small, optimization cycles were slow, and traditional performance marketing playbooks didn't apply.</div>
        </div>
        <div id="car-pocn-2" class="car-content" style="display:none">
          <div class="car-content-label">02 · Action</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">Sole programmatic strategist across up to 30 concurrent campaigns, plus a platform migration.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">Owned full programmatic strategy and execution across up to 30 concurrent campaigns spanning multiple therapeutic areas — segmenting NP and PA audiences for precision targeting and tailored messaging. Mid-tenure, led the migration from a third-party DSP to an internal platform, working directly with product and analytics teams to ship improvements based on real campaign-operator feedback.</div>
        </div>
        <div id="car-pocn-3" class="car-content" style="display:none">
          <div class="car-content-label">03 · Result</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">$1.7M+ managed. 50+ therapies. Significant platform cost savings.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">Over 26 months, managed $1.7M+ in total media spend across up to 30 concurrent campaigns, maintaining stable performance across a compliance-constrained clinical audience for the full duration of the engagement. The DSP migration drove significant annual cost savings while improving operational control and campaign scalability. Recommended a junior email marketing hire who is still employed at POCN.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section" style="border-bottom:none">
    <hr class="cs-rule" />
    <div class="next-prev">
      <a class="nav-card" href="/work/scandalous/"><div class="nav-card-dir">← Previous</div><div class="nav-card-title">Scandalous — Brand system</div><div class="nav-card-tag">Brand · GTM</div></a>
      <a class="nav-card right" href="/work/sigil/"><div class="nav-card-dir">Next →</div><div class="nav-card-title">SIGIL — GTM for original IP</div><div class="nav-card-tag">GTM · Brand</div></a>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-row"><a class="btn" href="/work/">← All case studies</a></div>
  </div>

</Base>
